Associate Justice:
And to the American people, I am
humbled by

01:43.270 --> 01:46.073 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the trust placed in me today.

01:46.106 --> 01:51.545 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
