all my powers
permit to be a faithful servant
of the Constitution

01:57.584 --> 01:59.419 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and laws of this great nation.

01:59.453 --> 02:04.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And we will take
a closer look
at the impact Justice Gorsuch
could have on

02:04.291 --> 02:07.561 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the high court a little later in
the program.

02:07.594 --> 02:12.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
