resources to
hide a romantic affair with an
aide.

02:19.072 --> 02:24.244 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jail records in Montgomery
County showed that
Bentley was booked today on two
campaign and

02:24.277 --> 02:25.645 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ethics charges.

02:25.679 --> 02:30.817 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
