Kay Ivey, is
expected to succeed him.

02:30.851 --> 02:35.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Don Dailey, who is the host of
Alabama Public
TV's "Capital Journal," has been
following

02:35.422 --> 02:36.490 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
