accused of.

02:40.961 --> 02:45.699 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DON DAILEY, Alabama Public TV:
All these charges,
as you mentioned, relate to his
alleged inappropriate

02:45.732 --> 02:49.736 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
