initiated
impeachment articles against the
governor.

02:54.608 --> 02:59.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, as a matter of fact,
hearings in those
articles of impeachment started
today, while,

02:59.446 --> 03:05.385 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
at the same time, officials were
behind closed
doors negotiating a resignation
deal with

03:05.419 --> 03:10.690 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Governor Bentley under which he
would plead
to lesser charges, thus the
campaign finance

03:10.724 --> 03:12.125 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
charges that you talked about.

03:12.159 --> 03:15.529 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now, the governor
has denied
this for the longest time.

03:15.562 --> 03:16.530 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
