done nothing
illegal in the furtherance of
that alleged

03:35.449 --> 03:37.117 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
affair.

03:37.150 --> 03:41.321 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And since it came
out so many
months ago, why, Don Dailey, has
it taken

03:41.354 --> 03:43.290 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
