04:16.256 --> 04:19.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DON DAILEY: He had to go to the
Montgomery
County Jail to be booked and
fingerprinted

04:19.759 --> 04:24.397 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
