04:49.689 --> 04:53.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Don Dailey with
Alabama Public
Television, we thank you very
much.

04:53.994 --> 04:55.862 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DON DAILEY: Thank you, Judy.

