role in the

22:51.370 --> 22:53.305 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
outcome of some very important
cases.

22:53.339 --> 22:55.174 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right, and
let's look at
some of them.

22:55.207 --> 22:58.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
