23:36.081 --> 23:37.316 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARCIA COYLE: It did.

23:37.349 --> 23:39.251 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it's been hanging in the
court since early
December.

23:39.285 --> 23:43.155 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we're not quite sure what
