good reason for you to have a
concealed carry

23:56.502 --> 23:58.637 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
gun, a permit for that.

23:58.671 --> 24:02.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right, and
then, next week,
he starts hearing cases for the
first time,

24:02.141 --> 24:03.108 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
right?

24:03.142 --> 24:04.843 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARCIA COYLE: Yes.

24:04.877 --> 24:07.646 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And the biggest
one next week
is a church and state separation
case out

24:07.680 --> 24:09.415 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
