24:09.448 --> 24:12.718 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE: That's right, and
it involves
Trinity Lutheran Church of
Missouri, which

24:12.751 --> 24:19.758 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
