25:12.544 --> 25:13.512 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE: Immigration.

25:13.545 --> 25:15.481 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Right, the executive order on
immigration.

25:15.514 --> 25:20.686 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
