around them.

37:59.244 --> 38:04.482 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: One young
woman that Quao
has mentored is Narkie Agbettor,
another Ashesi

38:04.516 --> 38:06.184 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
