solutions to every problem out
there.

38:22.567 --> 38:24.702 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It requires thinking.

38:24.736 --> 38:31.009 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, you want to be successful
and you want
to be ethical as well.

38:31.042 --> 38:36.381 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Patrick
Awuah knows that
his young, idealistic graduates,
many who

38:36.414 --> 38:41.619 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
